org.rdkit.knime.nodes.rmsdfilter

Class RDKitRMSDFilterNodeDialog

  • java.lang.Object
    • DefaultNodeSettingsPane
      • org.rdkit.knime.nodes.rmsdfilter.RDKitRMSDFilterNodeDialog

  • public class RDKitRMSDFilterNodeDialog
extends DefaultNodeSettingsPane
    NodeDialog for the "RDKitRMSDFilter" Node. Calculates the RMSD value for RDKit molecules and filters them based on a threshold value. This node dialog derives from DefaultNodeSettingsPane which allows creation of a simple dialog with standard components. If you need a more complex dialog please derive directly from org.knime.core.node.NodeDialogPane.
    Author:
    Manuel Schwarze
